'''伊戈尔·科尼''' （{{lang-ru|'''Игорь Яковлевич Крутой'''}}，{{bd|1954年|7月29日}}），[[烏克蘭族|乌克兰裔]][[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]][[作曲家|作曲家]]，[[演员|演员]]和[[音乐制作人|音乐制作人]]<ref>Е. В. Коровкина ''Кто есть кто в мире: 1500 имен'' 2003 p754 (Lengthy article in Russian ''Who's Who'')</ref> ，曾为[[普加乔娃|普加乔娃]]、[[瓦列莉娅|瓦列莉娅]]、[[阿尔苏|阿尔苏]]等歌星作曲。于1989年获列宁共产主义青年团奖章<ref name="biograph.ru">{{cite web |url=http://www.biograph.ru/bank/krutoi.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-12-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110912074232/http://www.biograph.ru/bank/krutoi.htm |archivedate=2011-09-12 }}</ref>，1992年获俄罗斯功绩卓著的艺术活动家，俄罗斯人民演员<ref name="biograph.ru"/>，乌克兰人民演员<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oreanda.ru/ru/news/20110825/culture/article574077/|title=Игорь Крутой стал "Народным артистом" Украины|work=ИА Ореанда-Новости|accessdate=2012-03-09|archive-date=2014-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413143711/http://www.oreanda.ru/ru/news/20110825/culture/article574077/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://novoteka.ru/sevent/10325373|title=Новотека: Новости - В Севастополе пройдёт Всероссийский турнир по смешанному боевому единоборству (ММА) среди правоохранителей|publisher=|accessdate=2012-03-09|archive-date=2012-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120425051339/http://novoteka.ru/sevent/10325373|dead-url=yes}}</ref>称号。伊戈尔在[[曼哈顿|曼哈顿]][[广场酒店|广场酒店]]购买了当时[[纽约|纽约]]最贵的单身公寓，1 Central Park South Realty LLC名下价值4千8百万的1207号和1209号房间。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ny.curbed.com/archives/2011/04/04/recordbreaking_plaza_condo_sale_is_now_official.php |title=Record-Breaking Plaza Condo Sale is Now Official |accessdate=2012-03-09 |archive-date=2012-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120106122655/http://ny.curbed.com/archives/2011/04/04/recordbreaking_plaza_condo_sale_is_now_official.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nypost.com/p/news/business/realestate/residential/exclusive_russian_composer_lands_oiWYcIFoCUodva7taQ0mGK#ixzz1HWeoZsX4|title=EXCLUSIVE: Russian composer lands Plaza Hotel condo for record-setting $48M price tag|date=2011-03-24|work=New York Post|accessdate=2012-03-09|archive-date=2012-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104072147/http://www.nypost.com/p/news/business/realestate/residential/exclusive_russian_composer_lands_oiWYcIFoCUodva7taQ0mGK#ixzz1HWeoZsX4|dead-url=no}}</ref>

